{`Props Interface for Greeting`} {`The user property has the following attributes: `} {`name`} {`username`} {`email`} {`Id`} {`departments.`} {`You can play with this component by deleting "user" in the playground and replacing it with a variable like:`} {`testName = {name: "Jarod Smith"} `} {`That will allow you to customize the displayed name (you can copy and paste that code and replace the user variable).`}
